        i0.ɵɵelementStart(238, "p", 12);
        i0.ɵɵtext(239, " Colleen Cole is an avid tabletop and PC gamer, model, sci-fi lover and comic enthusiast with a BA in Theatre. Colleen naturally gravitated to the world of cosplay almost ten years ago. You may remember her as Elvira and the Hellraiser Female Cenobite plus other favorite cosplays include Lady Death, Vampirella and Red Sonja. She's currently working on cosplays for the upcoming show plus Colleen will be a judge at our COFOH Gore Galore Costume Extravaganza at Colorado Festival of Horror Funhouse 2022! ");
